author: Misty L. Randolph
title: Misty L. Randolph
text: I have not used this site before but have been curious to check it out more than once. Wanting to name a STAR after my niece Jayda she is 5 yrs old and has special needs due to Cask gene mutation ( has to do with chromesones ) she brings the joy to each and every day. Lights up the sun,moon and STARS with her laugh and smile!
